status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.
status.name: Resolved

fields.description:
We will update the datalayer targeting ND Landing Page iteration AB testing. We will do grey release first so [~aholhos] can implement GTM before we kick off AB testing. 

 

===========

Here is the dataLayer Document for New Developments Landing page:
[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1tIJDs9xe3y1rFceUi_xt4okpnK50n3bepKA39mlHcvA/edit]

And here is the dataLayer Document for New Developments VIP page:
[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1corQEgJbSdsCr4BUuRk-3kTTIIMA9LYEeTRs1mP1l94/edit#|https://docs.google.com/document/d/1corQEgJbSdsCr4BUuRk-3kTTIIMA9LYEeTRs1mP1l94/edit]

comments.body: [~ropetrescu] do we need any enhancement for New Development - landing page
A lot, actually. I will make a list, and we can decide together on what is relevant + doable for now.

[~aparambath] we are thinking of assigning different pagetype to RE VIP, Project VIP, Unit VIP and Regular VIP. Wonder who from DWH we should talk to about this change? or we should avoid using eCG standard CD and use another CD for this purpose?

Here is the dataLayer Document for New Developments Landing page:
[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1tIJDs9xe3y1rFceUi_xt4okpnK50n3bepKA39mlHcvA/edit]

And here is the dataLayer Document for New Developments VIP page:
[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1corQEgJbSdsCr4BUuRk-3kTTIIMA9LYEeTRs1mP1l94/edit#|https://docs.google.com/document/d/1corQEgJbSdsCr4BUuRk-3kTTIIMA9LYEeTRs1mP1l94/edit]

Thank you!

[~aholhos] [~ropetrescu] below info are still not available for implementation:

For New Developments Landing

[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1tIJDs9xe3y1rFceUi_xt4okpnK50n3bepKA39mlHcvA/edit]

t: [Ad Type],

lpdt: [Ad Last Published Date], //the date of last published ad

cdt: [Ad Creation Date],

  

For New Development VIP

[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1corQEgJbSdsCr4BUuRk-3kTTIIMA9LYEeTRs1mP1l94/edit]

t: [Ad Type],

lpdt: [Ad Last Published Date],


BTW, are we already confirm that using pVIP and uVIP for p.t ? please confirm

Thanks, [~justin].
 * For the dates variables, it's fine, let's leave them out for now. I think we will be able to capture that once we switch pVIP to Ad ID.
 * [~aholhos] - can you confirm why we need [Ad Type]? It's not part of the requirements I built, but maybe I'm missing something.
 * Yes, we are good to change p.t to pVIP and uVIP, respectively. Please reflect the change in the implementation.

FYI [~jerome]

I checked and [Ad Type] was created on the first dataLayer document for VIP, right now is not present in the dataLayer so we are not using it and I can confirm we don't need it in the dataLayer for now.
Thank you!

Testing pass, and automation has updated on branch: 

ULIVZ-37637-ND-Datalayer-Refactor
